query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 5 AND q1.favorite_count <= 5000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('gis',
'salesforce',
'superuser')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('macos',
'windows-7')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.upvotes >= 1 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Benefactor',
'Beta',
'Constituent',
'Favorite Question',
'Investor',
'Mortarboard',
'Organizer',
'Peer Pressure',
'Quorum',
'Self-Learner',
'Taxonomist')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
